KitKat::

She opened her link, "Koj, Inu, I am ready to talk now if you wish to 
talk."

She heard the message from Destructor, "Your what? Get you jet 
blaster back here and we'll move then. But I need you to tell me what 
in the pit is going on first there."

She walked to the bridge where she saw Quickstrike. "Holy Matrix! 
Quickstrike!" She was overwhelmed with the site of her old friend. 
She put a soft hand on his shoulder. "Oh, it's great to see you 
again. I thought you were killed. Here, have a seat."  She offered 
him the seat next to her captain's chair. "Please, tell me what on 
earth happened. Gosh, it's great to see you. The old pack, together 
at last. I remember you showing me the ropes when I first joined."

She got Cerberus transmission. She sighed. "Yes, please contact me on 
my main comp." She sent the order for a base to base teleconference.

She then got Magmatron's transmission. She send him the orders for 
abase to base teleconference. "Please contact me when you can."
